data.description: Step into a lifestyle of comfort, style, and Florida living at its finest! Welcome to your dream home in the desirable Timber Pond neighborhood! This immaculate 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom oasis is a move-in-ready gem that combines comfort and style. Boasting a spacious 1647 sqft of living space, this residence is perfect for families and entertainers alike. As you step through the tile entryway, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail. The exterior of the home has been recently painted, adding to its charming curb appeal. Inside, the open floor plan seamlessly connects the formal dining area to the family room, creating a welcoming atmosphere for gatherings. The one-step sunken living room features vaulted ceilings and stunning tile flooring, creating a unique and elegant space. French doors lead from the living room to the inviting pool and paver patio, providing a perfect blend of indoor and outdoor living. The heart of the home is the eat-in kitchen, adorned with stainless steel appliances, chic gray cabinets, and a breakfast bar. The adjacent laundry room, with ample storage space, is located directly off the kitchen for added convenience and practicality to the daily routine. The master bedroom is a true retreat with tile flooring, a spacious walk-in closet, and an ensuite bath showcasing a single sink and a tiled stand-up shower. Bedrooms 1 and 2 feature laminate flooring, offering a cozy and low-maintenance living space. The guest bath echoes the same quality with a single sink and a tiled stand-up shower. Step into the backyard, where the entire space is paved and fenced, eliminating the need for tedious lawn maintenance. The saltwater pool, complete with an outdoor shower, offers the perfect spot to cool off on warm Florida days. But wait, there's more! Discover a versatile shed on the side of the home, fully insulated and drywalled, featuring two windows and a wall AC unit. Currently used as a 4th bedroom, this space can adapt to your needs—a guest room, home office, or functional storage area. Rest easy knowing that a new roof was installed in May 2023, adding to the home's value and longevity. Best of all, there's no HOA, giving you the freedom to make this house your home without restrictions. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Timber Pond haven your own; schedule your showing today!
